      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 3 上六</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 3 上六</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>上六，乘馬班如，泣血漣如。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The topmost SIX, divided, shows (its subject) with the horses of his chariot obliged to retreat, and weeping tears of blood in streams.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
